                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-551-18720708 t18720708-551-punishment-39"></join>Seven Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esq.</hi>
